ntinuing to demonstrate what I know.\u003C/em\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cem\u003E And though my days in the arena are past, \u003C/em\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cem\u003E My exploits stand the test of time.\u003C/em\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cem\u003E And now I help others develop their talents,\u003C/em\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cem\u003E Perhaps theirs will one day surpass mine.\u003C/em\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003ENo guesses yet, just reposting the riddle to the new page.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Xannari Ferrows","CreatedById":125369,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-04-08T22:54:33Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cem\u003EA Pencil?\u003C/em\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Deutherius","CreatedById":125381,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-04-08T23:39:31Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003ECould it be Sergey Bubka?\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cblockquote\u003E\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003E\u003Cem\u003EMy weapon of choice; a long slender staff,\u003C/em\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cem\u003E That I used to vanquish my foes.\u003C/em\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003EPole vaulter, and a very successful one.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E \u003C/p\u003E\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003E\u003Cem\u003EWhen they were beaten, I earned treasures fine\u003C/em\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cem\u003E By continuing to demonstrate what I know.\u003C/em\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003EBroke the pole vaulting record 35 times total.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E \u003C/p\u003E\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003E\u003Cem\u003EAnd though my days in the arena are past, \u003C/em\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cem\u003E My exploits stand the test of time.\u003C/em\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003ERetired from pole vaulting in 2001, but left behind a lot of work on the Petrov/Bubka technical model, which is still used today and considered to be great. \u003Csup\u003E[\u003C/sup\u003E\u003Cem\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022text-decoration:underline;\u0022\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022color:#0000ff;\u0022\u003E\u003Csup\u003Ecitation needed\u003C/sup\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/em\u003E\u003Csup\u003E]\u003C/sup\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E \u003C/p\u003E\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003E\u003Cem\u003EAnd now I help others develop their talents,\u003C/em\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cem\u003E Perhaps theirs will one day surpass mine.\u003C/em\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003EHe is now a vice-president and a chairman for the International Association of Athletics Federations, which holds a lot of athletic competitions, inspiring new athletes worldwide.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EDisclaimer: I am not a great fan of sports and everything I know about this guy was extracted from wikipedia - sorry if I got anything wrong \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"JebNeedsHelp","CreatedById":117002,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-04-09T04:01:07Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EDeutherius has got it. I was really hoping one of my riddles might make it 24 hours this time. This was the first one I wrote all by myself - what did you think?\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"vexx32","CreatedById":12283,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-04-09T08:53:45Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003ESeeing as I don\u0027t follow any kind of sports, that was certainly very obscure to me, haha. Not bad at all \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Deutherius","CreatedById":125381,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-04-09T12:52:42Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EIt was obscure, but researchable - you just had to figure out what \u003Cem\u003Elong slender staff\u003C/em\u003E means \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_tongue.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:P\u0022\u003E I liked it.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EI\u0027ll try to post a new riddle sometime today \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Ethanadams","CreatedById":136913,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-04-09T12:57:45Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EIs it the master sword?\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Xannari Ferrows","CreatedById":125369,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-04-09T14:26:45Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022vexx32\u0022 data-cite=\u0022vexx32\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003ESeeing as I don\u0027t follow any kind of sports, that was certainly very obscure to me, haha. Not bad at all \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003EI hear ya. Corns just start flyin\u0027 everywhere.\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}